graph TD
    Start([Workflow Request]) --> Mode{Execution Mode}
    
    Mode -->|Create New| Record[Start Recording]
    Mode -->|Run Existing| Load[Load Workflow]
    Mode -->|Auto-detect| Suggest[Pattern Detection]
    
    Record --> Capture[Capture Tool Calls]
    Capture --> Analyze[Analyze Patterns]
    Analyze --> Extract[Extract Parameters]
    Extract --> Create[Create Definition]
    Create --> Save[Save to Library]
    
    Load --> Validate[Validate Definition]
    Validate --> ValidParams[Validate Parameters]
    ValidParams --> Order[Calculate Execution Order]
    Order --> Execute[Execute Steps]
    
    Execute --> Step{For Each Step}
    Step --> CheckDeps[Check Dependencies]
    CheckDeps --> Resolve[Resolve Parameters]
    Resolve --> CallTool[Call Tool]
    CallTool --> Retry{Success?}
    
    Retry -->|No| RetryLogic[Apply Retry Policy]
    RetryLogic --> CallTool
    Retry -->|Yes| StepResult[Store Result]
    
    StepResult --> MoreSteps{More Steps?}
    MoreSteps -->|Yes| Step
    MoreSteps -->|No| ProcessOutput[Process Outputs]
    
    ProcessOutput --> End([Workflow Complete])
    
    Suggest --> Candidates[Generate Candidates]
    Candidates --> Present[Present to User]
    
    style Start fill:#4caf50
    style End fill:#4caf50
    style Execute fill:#ff9800
    style CallTool fill:#2196f3
